{"tid":1842742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【阿斗求簽記】鄉議局於沙田車公廟為香港求得第92簽中簽","createTime":"2020-01-26T01:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T01:11:24.000Z","uid":131892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a58267e1b9789e00c4dc6eee1d606c180085d7e6","tid":1842742,"uid":131892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:17:24.000Z","msg":"簽文：人生何在逞英豪，天理人情只要公；天眼恢恢疏不漏，定然作福福來縱。<br />\n<br />\n解簽：家宅平平，作福加增，自身平安，婚姻成合<br />\n<br />\n斷簽：家宅裝風光，占病作福，自身不吉，出入不安，婚姻不合，求財無，外強中乾，有私無公，上天示警，不然災星<br />\n<br />\n家宅：平平<br />\n<br />\n出行：遠行合宜<br />\n<br />\n姻緣：可成<br />\n<br />\n行人：有訊息<br />\n<br />\n生育：可得身孕<br />\n<br />\n訴訟：以和為貴<br />\n<br />\n事業：看準時機<br />\n<br />\n搬遷：吉方為佳<br />\n<br />\n自身：積德修身<br />\n<br />\n疾病：可痊癒<br />\n<br />\n財運：尚可"},{"pid":"b1b1ddbcd799840a8b19d0d7dd935fe80cb55e5c","tid":1842742,"uid":62350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:18:46.000Z","msg":"香港俾上面中出到有咗"},{"pid":"6ba983c0b6ed5a7b3f207722eb65511a852acbf2","tid":1842742,"uid":131892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:19:35.000Z","msg":"積德修身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a998701c7844392211b67e1059170f237edb468","tid":1842742,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:19:59.000Z","msg":"頭兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />車公"},{"pid":"d921255122a0d5f38ae888816edf362a3b22ee13","tid":1842742,"uid":63119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:20:17.000Z","msg":"點解準到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1038b05a2b6a2e85f9b2e2619cdad6ca91a6ca5","tid":1842742,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:23:38.000Z","msg":"天網恢恢 疏不漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77ccdc73f23d36c948a6a09ad3f27433d4fb29d","ti